<H4><A href="" name=fletching><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">Part 6: Fletching</SPAN></A><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H4>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Skill Requirement:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"> (220 Fletching assumed).<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Flag Requirement</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">: Rallos Zek and Solusek Ro?<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Commentary:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"> <I>None, as of yet.</I><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Original text:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">You say, 'I am skilled with a fletching knife'<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Aid Grimel says 'Aye I can see you are skilled with the fletching knife ____. It is good too, I need to replace Councilman Taldarius's bow from Plane of Air. Combine a planing tool, two wind metal bow cams, an air arachnid silk string, a featherwood staff and the signet. I hope the bow will be up to his standards, he sure loved his old bow.'<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Return to him with the signet featherwood bow in order to receive the runed signet<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Item Statistics: <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
