<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=9522&amp;menustr="><SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-ansi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Signet Featherwood Bow</SPAN></A></SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><BR>MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <BR>Slot: RANGE<BR>WT: 3.0 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: LARGE<BR>Class: NONE<BR>Race: NONE<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Recipes </SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
