<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Wind Cams: </SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">(Toolbox, ? trivial) <BR>Wind Cam Bolts? <BR>Wind <st1:place w:st="on">Cam</st1:place> Gears? <BR>Jar of Clockwork Grease <BR>Wind <st1:place w:st="on">Cam</st1:place> Parts <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
