</SPAN></DIV>
<H4><A href="" name=baking><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">Part 7: Baking</SPAN></A><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></H4>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Skill requirement:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"> ? Baking (220 Baking assumed).<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Flag requirement:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"> Rallos Zek<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Finally, the last monster. Baking. This was one of the most annoying recipes for folks to figure out. So when you make it, thank the people who spent the months combining and researching and just smashing their heads against their monitors figuring it out for you. Combine three of the Bristlebane Party Platters and your signet in the Satchel he gives you.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Original Text:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">You say, 'I am a Master Chef'<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Aid Grimel says 'When we adventure in the Planes there is only one meal that keeps us in top fighting shape. It is called a Bristlebane's Party Platter. Unfortunately the platter is awkward and not easy to adventure with so you need to place them in this satchel. I know not how to make the Platter, a rather nice female Halfling cleric used to deliver them to us. Quite an amazing lass to be braving so many of the Planes by herself. We chatted a bit last time she was here about her next trip she was planning on taking. She was going to spend time in Plane of Justice, twice as long as the other Planes. From there she was going to the river in Nightmare. After departing the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:PlaceType w:st="on">land</st1:PlaceType> of <st1:PlaceName w:st="on">Terris Thule</st1:PlaceName></st1:place> she was going to visit the home of the God who was once tormented by Terris. After picking up a few baskets from a friend, she was off to the home of the Triumvirate. Alas! Word made it back to me she was crushed by a Regrua while hunting for the dreaded beast's claws! Combine three of the platters and the signet inside the satchel.'<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Turn in text:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Aid Grimel says 'Truly amazing! Now the Councilman and I can be off on our expedition to the Elemental Planes!' He takes out a tool and marks his signet before handing it to you, 'Before we depart you may want to ask the Councilman about the signet.'<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Items given to you by Grimel:<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=8470&amp;menustr="><SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-ansi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Field Satchel</SPAN></A></SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><BR>Container: CLOSED.<BR>LORE ITEM NO DROP <BR>WT: 0.5 &nbsp;&nbsp;Weight Reduction: 0%<BR>Capacity: 4 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size Capacity: GIANT<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Item Statistics:</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=8512&amp;menustr="><FONT size=1><SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-ansi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Bristlebanes Party Platter</SPAN></FONT></A></SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><BR><FONT size=1>NO DROP <BR>This is a Miraculous Meal<BR>STR: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;DEX: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;STA: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;WIS: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;INT: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;AGI: +10 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>HP: +75 &nbsp;&nbsp;MANA: +75 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>WT: 8.5 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: GIANT<BR>Class: ALL<BR>Race: ALL</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"></SPAN><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><BR><B><A href="http://www.eqtraders.com/items/show_item.php?item=9523&amp;menustr="><FONT size=1><SPAN style="COLOR: black; mso-ansi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Marked Runed Signet</SPAN></FONT></A></B><BR><FONT size=1>MAGIC ITEM LORE ITEM NO DROP <BR>Slot: EAR<BR>AC: 17<BR>STR: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;DEX: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;STA: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;WIS: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;INT: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;AGI: +17 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>HP: +115 &nbsp;&nbsp;MANA: +115 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>SV FIRE: +12 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV DISEASE: +12 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV COLD: +12 &nbsp;&nbsp;SV MAGIC: +12 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>SV POISON: +12 &nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>Effect: Regeneration (Worn)<BR>WT: 1.5 &nbsp;&nbsp;Size: TINY<BR>Class: ALL<BR>Race: ALL<o:p></o:p></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Recipes</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P><B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt">Bristlebane's Party Platter(Tanaan Oven/Collapsible Spit, &gt;250 Trivial)</SPAN></B><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><BR>Justice Fruit Pie<BR>Justice Fruit Pie<BR>Slarghilug Stuffed Poppers<BR>Hero <st1:place w:st="on">Sandwich</st1:place><BR>Bucket of Crab Legs<BR>Picnic Basket <o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<DIV align=center class=MsoNormal style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><SPAN style="COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: Garamond; FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">
